dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1.GDB feature class had undefined projection, now has "GCS_WGS_1984" projection. 2. Converted Admin2 and 3 names to Proper Case. 3. Found and fixed multipart sliver errors in Admin3 "Cachipo", "San Antonio", "Concepción" and "Manuel Felipe Rugeles". 4. 30 small nesting errors between admin layers were fixed.
